  File                     = {::},
  ISBN                     = {0270-6474},
  ISSN                     = {1529-2401},
  Keywords                 = {ag,and posterior middle temporal,angular gyrus,but their individual,coactivated during neuroimaging studies,conceptual processing,control,functional dissociation between the,gyrus,in,pmtg,posterior middle temporal gyrus,semantic,significance statement,these sites are often,transcranial magnetic stimulation,using semantic tasks,we demonstrate a novel},
